					    <article id="post-27822" class="post-27822 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-culture category-featured-post category-links tag-arthur-meursault tag-ccp tag-party-members clearfix" role="article">
						
						    <header class="article-header">
							
							    <h1 class="h2"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/2017/10/like-a-hammer-to-the-head-review-arthur-meursalts-party-members/" rel="bookmark" title="“Like a hammer to the head” Review: Arthur Meursalt’s  ‘Party Members’">“Like a hammer to the head” Review: Arthur Meursalt’s  ‘Party Members’</a></h1>
                  <p class="byline vcard">By <span class="author"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/author/rfh/" title="Posts by By Carlos Ottery" rel="author">By Carlos Ottery</a></span> &nbsp; Comments: <a href="http://beijingcream.com/2017/10/like-a-hammer-to-the-head-review-arthur-meursalts-party-members/#comments">3</a> &nbsp; <time class="updated" datetime="2017-10-27" pubdate>October 27, 2017 9:40 am</time></p>
						
