						    <header class="article-header">
							
							    <h1 class="h2"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/2017/07/liu-xiaobo-is-dead-and-the-beijing-sky-is-in-uproar/" rel="bookmark" title="Liu Xiaobo Is Dead, And The Beijing Sky Is In Uproar">Liu Xiaobo Is Dead, And The Beijing Sky Is In Uproar</a></h1>
                  <p class="byline vcard">By <span class="author"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/category/by-anthony-tao" title="Posts by Anthony Tao" rel="author">Anthony Tao</a></span> &nbsp; Comments: <a href="http://beijingcream.com/2017/07/liu-xiaobo-is-dead-and-the-beijing-sky-is-in-uproar/#comments">2</a> &nbsp; <time class="updated" datetime="2017-07-13" pubdate>July 13, 2017 11:38 pm</time></p>
						
