						    <header class="article-header">
							
							    <h1 class="h2"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/2016/04/dfxj-uyghur-urbanism-in-recent-modernist-poetry/" rel="bookmark" title="Dispatches From Xinjiang: Uyghur Urbanism in Recent Modernist Poetry">Dispatches From Xinjiang: Uyghur Urbanism in Recent Modernist Poetry</a></h1>
                  <p class="byline vcard">By <span class="author"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/category/by-beige-wind" title="Posts by Beige Wind" rel="author">Beige Wind</a></span> &nbsp; Comments: <a href="http://beijingcream.com/2016/04/dfxj-uyghur-urbanism-in-recent-modernist-poetry/#comments">0</a> &nbsp; <time class="updated" datetime="2016-04-21" pubdate>April 21, 2016 3:00 pm</time></p>
						
