                  <p class="byline vcard">By <span class="author"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/category/by-pavoir-sponze" title="Posts by Pavoir Sponze" rel="author">Pavoir Sponze</a></span> &nbsp; Comments: <a href="http://beijingcream.com/2016/03/mega-fail-how-a-bestselling-american-futurist-lost-his-way-in-china/#comments">8</a> &nbsp; <time class="updated" datetime="2016-03-1" pubdate>March 1, 2016 1:14 pm</time></p>
						
