						    <header class="article-header">
							
							    <h1 class="h2"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/2015/12/its-a-white-christmas-in-beijing/" rel="bookmark" title="It&#8217;s A White Christmas In Beijing">It&#8217;s A White Christmas In Beijing</a></h1>
                  <p class="byline vcard">By <span class="author"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/category/by-anthony-tao" title="Posts by Anthony Tao" rel="author">Anthony Tao</a></span> &nbsp; Comments: <a href="http://beijingcream.com/2015/12/its-a-white-christmas-in-beijing/#comments">1</a> &nbsp; <time class="updated" datetime="2015-12-25" pubdate>December 25, 2015 5:25 pm</time></p>
						
						    </header> <!-- end article header -->
					
						    <section class="entry-content clearfix">
							<div style="float: left;">
								<a href="http://beijingcream.com/2015/12/its-a-white-christmas-in-beijing/"><img width="230" height="172" src="http://beijingcream.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Beijing-Christmas-2016b-300x225.jpg" class="attachment-230x210 wp-post-image" alt="Beijing Christmas 2016b" /></a>
							</div>
							Happy holidays, everybody!							<a class="read-more" href="http://beijingcream.com/2015/12/its-a-white-christmas-in-beijing/">Read more &raquo;</a>
